<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<StimulusTransportBase xmlns:i="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/Tobii.Studio.Design.Transport">
  <Key>e259e5bd-040d-4981-8a76-fe7239a65248</Key>
  <Value i:type="InstructionsStimulusTransport">
    <Channel>WpfChannel</Channel>
    <Id>d2013b0c-d5a3-4048-b065-4963494d8d54</Id>
    <Name>Chatgpt-2</Name>
    <BackgroundColor xmlns:d2p1="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/Tobii.ApplicationFoundation">
      <d2p1:A>255</d2p1:A>
      <d2p1:B>211</d2p1:B>
      <d2p1:G>211</d2p1:G>
      <d2p1:R>211</d2p1:R>
    </BackgroundColor>
    <IsMouseCursorVisible>false</IsMouseCursorVisible>
    <Margin>4</Margin>
    <Markup>&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"&gt;&lt;html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /&gt;&lt;title&gt;Untitled&lt;/title&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;Stay seamlessly connected with the inDigi U-Watch Smart Watch, a cutting-edge wearable that extends the functionality of your smartphone right to your wrist. Designed with both style and technology in mind, this smartwatch features a sleek, minimalist aesthetic complemented by a high-resolution OLED screen that offers crisp visuals and vibrant displays.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;Key Features:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Bluetooth Connectivity: Easily connect the U-Watch with any Bluetooth-enabled device and experience the convenience of making and receiving calls directly from your wrist, thanks to its built-in microphone and speaker.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Comprehensive Compatibility: The smartwatch is fully compatible with Android 2.3+ and iOS 4.0+ devices, allowing you to sync your phonebook, call history, and messaging notifications. For Android users, additional features are available through the BTNotifier app.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; OLED Screen Display: Enjoy clear and bright visuals on the U-Watch&amp;rsquo;s OLED display, which enhances your interaction with notifications and apps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Integrated Phone Features: Manage calls with caller ID, utilize the watch as a wireless dialer, and stay on top of your schedule with features like an alarm, stopwatch, and remote notifications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Music Control: Control music playback on your phone directly from your wrist, perfect for both convenience and entertainment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Anti-Lost Alert: Never worry about leaving your phone behind. The U-Watch alerts you if your paired device is out of range, helping prevent loss or theft.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Multifunctional Utility: Beyond typical watch functions, it includes features like a ringtone &amp;amp; vibrate mode, built-in music player, and comprehensive tools like a stopwatch and alarm for everyday use.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 6.66px;margin-bottom: 6.66px;line-height: 1.5;text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Roboto';font-style: Normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;color: #000000;"&gt;Whether you&amp;rsquo;re a professional looking to streamline communication and notifications, or you simply want a reliable extension of your smartphone, the inDigi U-Watch is your ideal choice. It brings a blend of modern technology and classic watch functionality, perfect for anyone looking to enhance their tech-savvy lifestyle.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</Markup>
    <Resolution xmlns:d2p1="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/Tobii.ApplicationFoundation">
      <d2p1:Height>1080</d2p1:Height>
      <d2p1:Width>1920</d2p1:Width>
    </Resolution>
    <SupportsReadingResearch>true</SupportsReadingResearch>
  </Value>
</StimulusTransportBase>